2010-10-20, Shamelessly copied from my own project HUnit.

Testing
--------

Taken from ExtUtils::MakeMaker::FAQ:

    make realclean
    perl Makefile.PL INSTALL_BASE=/tmp
    make install
    export PERL5LIB=/tmp/lib/perl5
    /tmp/bin/amazong

Install
---------

perl Makefile.PL PREFIX=$HOME/local
(make test)
make install
(make clean)

